data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 3 1/2-bathroom home that offers a spacious and comfortable living environment. The heart of this residence is the generously sized eat-in kitchen with a large island and all appliances included, making it perfect for family gatherings and casual dining. You'll also find a separate dining area for more formal occasions and a cozy family room complete with a fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for your evenings. Additionally, there's a versatile flex room that can be used as a home office, playroom, or adapted to suit your lifestyle. The 4th bedroom has a private entrance off of the kitchen at the garage and features a full private bath, making it perfect for in-laws or young adults seeking privacy. This delightful home sits on a corner lot of just over an acre, featuring a professionally landscaped yard with a fire pit, providing an ideal outdoor space for relaxation and entertainment. The seller has taken great care of this home and loves the community but is relocating closer to family. The property boasts both upstairs and main level AC units that are approximately 2 years old, ensuring efficient climate control throughout the home. The washer and dryer, both less than 3 years old, and most of the furnishings can remain with the property, adding to your convenience. Located within an excellent school district and part of a wonderful swim and tennis community, this property is the perfect place to call home.
